# ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
# DeepProvenance — Environment Variables
# ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

# ── App ──────────────────────────────────────────────────
APP_NAME=DeepProvenance
APP_ENV=development
DEBUG=true
SECRET_KEY=your-secret-key-change-in-production
API_VERSION=v1
CORS_ORIGINS=http://localhost:5173,http://localhost:3000

# ── Database (PostgreSQL) ────────────────────────────────
DATABASE_URL=postgresql+asyncpg://deepprov:deepprov@localhost:5432/deepprovenance
POSTGRES_USER=deepprov
POSTGRES_PASSWORD=deepprov
POSTGRES_DB=deepprovenance

# ── Redis ────────────────────────────────────────────────
REDIS_URL=redis://localhost:6379/0
CELERY_BROKER_URL=redis://localhost:6379/1
CELERY_RESULT_BACKEND=redis://localhost:6379/2

# ── JWT Auth ─────────────────────────────────────────────
JWT_SECRET_KEY=your-jwt-secret-change-in-production
JWT_ALGORITHM=HS256
JWT_ACCESS_TOKEN_EXPIRE_MINUTES=30
JWT_REFRESH_TOKEN_EXPIRE_DAYS=7

# ── MinIO (S3-compatible storage) ────────────────────────
MINIO_ENDPOINT=localhost:9000
MINIO_ACCESS_KEY=minioadmin
MINIO_SECRET_KEY=minioadmin
MINIO_BUCKET=deepprovenance-media
MINIO_USE_SSL=false

# ── Pinecone (Vector DB) ────────────────────────────────
PINECONE_API_KEY=your-pinecone-api-key
PINECONE_ENVIRONMENT=us-east-1
PINECONE_INDEX_NAME=content-dna-registry

# ── Blockchain (Polygon zkEVM Testnet) ──────────────────
POLYGON_RPC_URL=https://rpc.cardona.zkevm-rpc.com
POLYGON_CHAIN_ID=2442
CONTRACT_ADDRESS=0x0000000000000000000000000000000000000000
DEPLOYER_PRIVATE_KEY=your-deployer-private-key

# ── ML Model ────────────────────────────────────────────
MODEL_PATH=./ml/checkpoints/vit_forgery_detector.pth
MODEL_NAME=google/vit-base-patch16-224
CONFIDENCE_THRESHOLD=0.7
DEMO_MODE=true

# ── Frontend ────────────────────────────────────────────
VITE_API_URL=http://localhost:8000
VITE_WS_URL=ws://localhost:8000
VITE_POLYGON_EXPLORER=https://cardona-zkevm.polygonscan.com
